Installation
$ brew install neovim/neovim/neovim

Linking configuration
$ ln -s ~/.vim ~/.config/nvim
$ ln -s ~/.vimrc ~/.config/nvim/init.vim

Python support
$ pip install neovim

Graphical Interface
$ brew tap rogual/neovim-dot-app
$ brew install --HEAD neovim-dot-app

Fixing configuration issues
if !has('nvim')
  set ttymouse=xterm2
endif


